Simple Banking Application
This simple 20-minute tutorial shows how to make a simple banking application that acts as a checking account. 
It utilizes print statements, if/else statements, strings, ints, methods, loops, and more. Using these techniques, 
the bank program created allows the user to deposit money, withdraw money, or check the balance of the account. 
This is definitely one of the easier projects for a beginner to do once they have learned some fundamental concepts.